{
  "texts": [
    "Identifying sections in clinical texts has been shown to enhance performance on several MIE tasks (Pomares-Quimbaya, Kreuzthaler, and Schulz 2019).",
    "However, this research field remains underdeveloped, partly due to the lack of benchmark datasets (cf.",
    "comprehensive survey Landolsi, Hlaoua, and Ben Romdhane 2023).",
    "Therefore, most studies focus on English clinical texts (Denny 2008; Edinger 2017).",
    "In-depth studies focusing on few-shot learning scenarios and prompting are still lacking (Ge 2023)."
  ]
}